productReviews.reviewText: The box this comes in is 3 meter by 5 foot and weights 11 kilogram.
My porcupine loves to play with it.
I tried to pepper it but got prune all over it.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This Dynamic keeps them away.
My co-worker Nile has one of these. He says it looks crooked.
